334
00:19:36.952 --> 00:19:37.252
Group.

335
00:19:42.832 --> 00:19:46.652
Immune checkpoint inhibitor have really transformed the

336
00:19:46.712 --> 00:19:50.252
treatment of melanoma patient in the past decade and achieved a

337
00:19:50.292 --> 00:19:54.222
substantial clinical benefit. Nevertheless, about 40% to

338
