353
00:20:47.752 --> 00:20:50.872
Our study cohort consists of 164

354
00:20:51.732 --> 00:20:55.352
cutaneous melanoma patients. Treatment in naive tumor

355
00:20:55.392 --> 00:20:58.542
samples was collected from those patient prospectively.

356
00:20:59.612 --> 00:21:00.552
Among the tumors,

357
00:21:01.632 --> 00:21:05.152
about 46% are primary tumor, and the rest are

358
00:21:05.172 --> 00:21:06.332
