359
00:21:07.272 --> 00:21:11.082
And consistent with literature finding, we observed a significant

360
00:21:11.132 --> 00:21:14.972
association with gender male and later tumor stage

361
00:21:15.052 --> 00:21:16.712
with worse survival outcome.

362
00:21:18.432 --> 00:21:21.932
So for majority of the tumors, we are able to collect

363
00:21:22.732 --> 00:21:26.492
13 different multi-omics layer profiles, including

364
00:21:26.552 --> 00:21:29.242
four PTM data, metabolics data, and

365
00:21:29.392 --> 00:21:33.332
