366
00:21:33.352 --> 00:21:36.792
state-of-the-art platforms, such that our

367
00:21:38.152 --> 00:21:41.912
omics data is of high quality and great

368
00:21:42.012 --> 00:21:44.702
depth of coverage across all of them.

369
00:21:47.592 --> 00:21:50.732
So based on the whole genome sequencing and whole exome sequencing data, we

370
00:21:50.772 --> 00:21:54.572
