374
00:22:05.912 --> 00:22:09.072
mutations, as well as CDKN2A deletions.

375
00:22:09.452 --> 00:22:12.992
And we don't observe significant differences between the primary

376
00:22:13.032 --> 00:22:16.552
tumors versus the metastasis tumors in terms of the DNA

377
00:22:16.612 --> 00:22:17.592
alteration pattern.

378
00:22:20.632 --> 00:22:24.092
We performed a comprehensive HLA-1 peptomics

379
00:22:24.172 --> 00:22:27.952
profiling using optimal LS tandem mass

380
00:22:27.992 --> 00:22:28.971
