00:22:37.192 --> 00:22:38.282
binding peptides.

384
00:22:39.152 --> 00:22:42.632
The non-chronical ORFs included in this database

385
00:22:43.312 --> 00:22:45.452
has supports from the rigorous

386
00:22:46.852 --> 00:22:49.892
evidence of translation from previous work.

387
00:22:50.532 --> 00:22:53.472
And using this pipeline, we identified more than

388
00:22:53.992 --> 00:22:57.252
300K unique HLA-1 binding peptides,

389
00:22:57.792 --> 00:23:01.512
and we further using very stringent criterion to remove the

390
00:23:01.552 --> 00:23:04.752
peptides that has been ever observed in normal tissue

391
00:23:04.852 --> 00:23:08.192
immunopeptidomics landscape. So this resulted in

392
00:23:09.052 --> 00:23:12.672
