398
00:23:32.992 --> 00:23:36.132
In our data, we observed a large variability of the

399
00:23:36.272 --> 00:23:39.852
HLA-1 peptide total counts across tumor samples.

400
00:23:40.752 --> 00:23:44.592
And the HLA-1 peptide total counts also

