633
00:36:20.952 --> 00:36:23.872
All right. So overall, breast cancer is the most common invasive cancer among

634
00:36:23.912 --> 00:36:27.822
women in the United States. It's estimated that one in eight will

635
00:36:27.832 --> 00:36:29.972
