00:40:07.172 --> 00:40:10.462
And then to assess adherence to each therapy, we use what's called a proportion of

703
00:40:10.532 --> 00:40:14.262
days covered metric. And so this means that for any given year, if a patient had

704
00:40:14.292 --> 00:40:17.872
