1932
01:49:09.324 --> 01:49:10.464
benefit from it.

1933
01:49:10.844 --> 01:49:11.044
Mm-hmm.

1934
01:49:11.144 --> 01:49:14.584
What you're showing us is that you can potentially sensitize-

1935
01:49:14.904 --> 01:49:15.284
Yes

1936
01:49:15.584 --> 01:49:17.804
