1962
01:50:27.784 --> 01:50:29.404
Yeah, that's really interesting.

1963
01:50:29.504 --> 01:50:33.444
I know right now everything has been using with inhibitor

1964
01:50:33.484 --> 01:50:34.384
has been in vivo.

1965
01:50:35.644 --> 01:50:39.244
But as far as application to patient samples, I'm

1966
